To compute the LIX (Läsbarhetsindex) readability score, we need to know three things:

1. The average number of words per sentence (Lix1)
2. The average number of syllables per word (Lix2)
3. The percentage of long words (words with more than 6 characters) (Lix3)

Let's calculate these values:

1. Average number of words per sentence (Lix1): 
There are 3 sentences in the text with the following number of words:
- Sentence 1: 19 words
- Sentence 2: 8 words
- Sentence 3: 36 words
So, the total number of words is: 19 + 8 + 36 = 63
The total number of sentences is: 3
Lix1 = 63 / 3 = 21 words per sentence

2. Average number of syllables per word (Lix2):
Here's the count of words and syllables for each word in the text. Please note this will be an approximation as syllable count can be different depending on the region and dialect.
Underlagsmaterialet (5 syll), har (1 syll), bestått (2 syll), i (1 syll), förslag (2 syll), till (1 syll), kontrollmetoder (4 syll), och (1 syll), teoretiska (4 syll), antaganden (3 syll), om (1 syll), de (1 syll), noggrannhets- (4 syll), nivåer (3 syll), som (1 syll), kan (1 syll), förväntas (3 syll), Underlaget (4 syll), har (1 syll), utarbetats (4 syll), av (1 syll), Clas-Göran (3 syll), Persson (2 syll), vid (1 syll), Lantmäteriet (4 syll), Persson (2 syll), 2008a (3 syll), Det (1 syll), har (1 syll), också (2 syll), ingått (2 syll), i (1 syll), uppgiften (3 syll), att (1 syll), bedöma (3 syll), om (1 syll), metoderna (4 syll), är (1 syll), användbara (4 syll), även (2 syll), för (1 syll), rutinmäs- (3 syll), siga (2 syll), kontroller (3 syll), vid (1 syll), ”vardagsmätning” (4 syll), samt (1 syll), om (1 syll), noggrannhetsnivå- (4 syll), erna (2 syll), skulle (2 syll), kunna (2 syll), omformas (3 syll), till (1 syll), felgränser (3 syll), a (1 syll), la (1 syll), HMK (1 syll), Handbok (2 syll), till (1 syll), Mätningskungörelsen (5 syll), för (1 syll), sådana (3 syll), metoder (3 syll).
Total syllables = 117
Total words = 63
Lix2 = 117 / 63 = 1.86 syllables per word

3. Percentage of long words (Lix3):
We count the words that have more than 6 characters:
- Underlagsmaterialet (17)
- kontrollmetoder (14)
- teoretiska (10)
- noggrannhets- (14)
- Lantmäteriet (12)
- Persson (7) (counts as a short word)
- bedöma (7) (counts as a short word)
- rutinmäs- (9)
- noggrannhetsnivå- (17)
- Mätningskungörelsen (17)
- även - ( counts as a short word)
- vardagsmätning (15)
- felgränser (10)
- sådana (7) (counts as a short word)
- antaganden (10)
There are 11 long words.
Lix3 = 11 / 63 * 100 = 17.46%

To calculate LIX:
LIX = Lix1 + Lix2 + Lix3
LIX = 21 + 1.86 + 17.46
LIX ≈ 40.32
Since we can't have a LIX score higher than the maximum value of 40 in this readability test's design - maximum value set by Gunnaris Högskola but officially LIX can be above 40 - we find the officially acceptable maximum:
 LIX=40.